text:
Raymond Michael Kethledge (born December 11, 1966) is an American judge. He is the United States Circuit Judge of the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit. He is a former law clerk for Associate Justice Anthony Kennedy of the Supreme Court of the United States.
Kethledge is on President Donald Trump's list of potential Supreme Court justices.
